          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mrs-irene-adams" title="Mrs Irene Adams">Mrs. Irene Adams (in the Chair)</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            Order.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
